SUMMARY:Free guided walks through Armstrong Redwoods in Guerneville
DESCRIPTION:Free guided tours at Armstrong Redwoods State Natural Reserve every Saturday & Sunday. \nJoin us for an easy\, docent-guided walk along the forest floor\, and learn about redwoods\, the history of the area\, its people\, plants\, and animals!  Meet in the front parking lot at 10AM next to the picnic tables.  Armstrong Redwoods\, 17000 Armstrong Woods Road\, Guerneville.  Map: https://maps.app.goo.gl/jnyfPDnHhSStJnBH7 \nIf your group size is larger than 10 (adults and children)\, please telephone 707-869-9177 ex 1. \nTour time: 2 hours\, and covers up to 2 miles. \nSee you in the forest!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/free-guided-walks-through-armstrong-redwoods-in-guerneville-38/
LOCATION:Armstrong Redwoods State Natural Reserve\, 17000 Armstrong Woods Rd\, Guerneville\, CA
CATEGORIES:Recreation
