SUMMARY:Second Annual Women's History Crawl at the Sonoma Barracks
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Women’s History Month and join us for the Second Annual Women’s History Crawl at Sonoma State Historic Park’s Sonoma Barracks! This in-person event will take you on a journey through the rich history of women in Sonoma County\, the Bay Area and beyond. Grab your friends and come crawl with us to learn about fabulous women\, and a chance to win great prizes!
