SUMMARY:Annual Lunar New Year FREE Community Celebration in Sonoma Valley
DESCRIPTION:The Center’s festivities will offer a variety of creative programming and artistic workshops throughout February and March. The Center will hold an exclusive live public performance from the Redwood Empire Chinese Association (RECA) and Hula Mai on Saturday\, March 7\, 2026. \nFree to all\, the Lunar New Year Community Day will begin at 12 PM with a traditional Chinese Calligraphy demonstration by Sonoma Valley Council Member Jack Ding and guest Gigi Tan Pfleger. The art activities will be followed by engaging performances by RECA’s own musical performers. \n12-3 PM AAPI Food Vendors and Makers\nWe are excited to welcome a variety of Bay Area AAPI food trucks and local vendors who will offer tasty options for purchase throughout the event.\nIncluding: Mr. Dim Sum\, Golden State Pickle Works\, Maison des Plaisances\, Valley Boba Craft Tea\, Square Peg Foundation\, and Author/Illustrator Anna Wong. \n12-1 PM Traditional Chinese Calligraphy\nPresented by Jack Ding and Gigi Tan Pfleger. \nChinese Mahjong Demonstration\nPresented by John Tan and Michael Gomez. \nChildren’s Crafts\nPresented by the Center’s Youth Arts Program. \n1-1:30 PM Dance Performance by Hula Mai\nHula Mai is the local Hawaiian performing arts group. Hula Mai was founded by Betty Ann Ka Ihilani Bruno. \n1:30-3 PM Performance by Redwood Empire Chinese Association\nRECA is a non-profit organization with the mission to preserve and share Chinese culture\, language\, and heritage. \nCategory: Festivals \nDate and Time: Saturday March 07\, 2026 at 12:00 pm to 3:00 pm \nVenue details: Sonoma Community Center\, 276 East Napa Street\, Sonoma\, California\, 95476\, United States
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/annual-lunar-new-year-free-community-celebration-in-sonoma-valley/
LOCATION:Sonoma Community Center\, 276 East Napa Street\, Sonoma\, 95476
CATEGORIES:Festival
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Lunar-New-Year-Celebration-Sonoma-s.jpg
GEO:38.2918;-122.453
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Sonoma Community Center 276 East Napa Street Sonoma 95476;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=276 East Napa Street:geo:-122.453,38.2918
END:VEVENT
