SUMMARY:TEDxSonomaCounty
DESCRIPTION:Mindshift: Power of Perspective invites our community to explore how changing the way we see the world can unlock new possibilities for connection\, creativity\, and progress. On March 7\, 2026\, at the Jackson Theater at Sonoma Country Day School\, a curated lineup of thinkers\, doers\, and performers will share ideas that challenge assumptions and reveal the power of reframing—from generational wisdom and digital culture to leadership\, resilience\, and the psychology of perception. Through compelling talks and moments of surprise and delight\, Mindshift is an invitation to pause\, look again\, and discover how a shift in perspective can change not only how we think\, but how we live. TEDxSonomaCounty is an independently organized TEDx event\, operating under license from TED.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/tedxsonomacounty/
LOCATION:Jackson Theater at Sonoma Country Day School\, 4400 Day School Place\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Other
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/TEDx-Sonoma-County-s.jpg
