SUMMARY:Canceled: Nature’s Delights: Community Artist Exhibition and Reception
DESCRIPTION:“Nature’s Delights” features a select range of diverse and underrepresented artists in our local communities\, celebrating the bounty of talent and art in our region. This includes artists from Raizes Collective. See the creative interpretations of our theme through beautifully painted and hand-crafted art. \nEnjoy tasty treats in an uplifting and welcoming atmosphere. Join the fun in our group art project\, materials are provided and all ages welcome. \nShowstoppers Artist Collective gallery features the creations of local artists in an uplifting community gallery and gathering place. Located in the cozy Co-Create space; boutique art\, photographs\, gifts and workshops are featured alongside a stunning space to connect and create\, while bringing art to life. Beautifully hand-crafted\, painted and homespun art will take center stage; as enlightening and educational art workshops\, talks and groups aim to inspire. Connect with others in our community to form valuable friendships and let your heart and imagination fly. Come take a picture with Cassie\, the life-like dog you simply have to see to believe. Woof!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/natures-delights-community-artist-exhibition-and-reception/
LOCATION:Showstoppers Artist Collective (in the Cozy Co-Create space)\, 186 N. Main Street\, Suite 110\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Art
GEO:38.40341;-122.82541
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Showstoppers Artist Collective (in the Cozy Co-Create space) 186 N. Main Street Suite 110 Sebastopol CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=186 N. Main Street\, Suite 110:geo:-122.82541,38.40341
END:VEVENT
