SUMMARY:Saturday Live Music at Spicy Vines feat. 7 Acre Holler
DESCRIPTION:Where unforgettable wines\, live music\, and good vibes come together. \nJoin us every Saturday from 3–6 PM at Spicy Vines for a tasting room experience like no other — where top local musicians from across the Bay Area meet our award-winning small-lot wines. From Rock & Roll and Blues to Jazz\, Bluegrass\, and Americana\, each weekend brings new sounds and new reasons to raise a glass. \n7 Acre Holler\nAcre Holleris Sonoma County–based duo Cori Wood and Layne Bowen\, blending rich harmonies with Appalachian-inspired folk and Americana. \nDetails\nNo cover. Walk-ins are welcome\, but this event tends to fill up quickly\, so we recommend making a reservation. We are dog and family friendly!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/saturday-live-music-at-spicy-vines-feat-7-acre-holler/
LOCATION:Spicy Vines\, 441 Healdsburg Ave.\, Healdsburg\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
