SUMMARY:The Arts Guild of Sonoma Presents: A Fresh New Season of Art
DESCRIPTION:Spring arrives with renewed creativity at the Arts Guild of Sonoma with A Fresh New Season of Art\, on view Thursday\, March 5 through Monday\, March 30\, 2026. The exhibition features paintings\, photography\, ceramics\, sculpture\, jewelry\, prints\, and artful gifts—all created by Sonoma-area fine artists.\nThe public is invited to a special reception on Saturday\, March 7\, from 5:00 to 7:00 PM\, celebrating featured Guest Artist Renate Kuprian\, a beloved art teacher at Sonoma Valley High School who will be exhibiting her own paintings/mixed media pieces.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-arts-guild-of-sonoma-presents-a-fresh-new-season-of-art/
