SUMMARY:The Michael Gaither Duo at The Block
DESCRIPTION:Michael Gaither is an award-winning songwriter based out of Santa Cruz CA. His songs alternate between the nostalgia of small-town life and the challenges of modern technology\, along with a good helping of observational humor. (He had a narrow brush with standup comedy in a previous life.) Michael’s latest record of original material – his fifth – is “Welcome Back: A Collection.” \nOnstage\, Michael’s shows are a combination of his fun original tunes\, stories with a backbeat and Americana with a small-town angle\, along with songs by artists who’ve influenced him. He’s always entertaining with lots of audience engagement. Michael is available as a solo performer or as a duo/trio/full band with his “New Best Friends” ensemble. And as a supporting act\, he’s opened for other artists including Steve Poltz\, Eilen Jewell and Janiva Magness.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-michael-gaither-duo-at-the-block/
LOCATION:The Block Petaluma\, 20 Grey Street\, Petaluma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.236416;-122.638896
