SUMMARY:Turn of the Century at the Penngrove Pub
DESCRIPTION:Originating from humble beginnings in a cramped garage\, as many great things do “Turn of the Century” is a dynamic party rock and roll cover band! With infectious energy and unwavering passion for music\, this powerhouse ensemble delivers high-octane renditions of chart-topping hits. From bars and clubs\, to private parties and corporate events\, Turn of the Century brings the party with them wherever they go. Reach out now for pricing options\, availability\, and a rockin’ good time!
